text: Georgy Baimakov (born 1 June 1894, date of death unknown) was a Russian swimmer. He competed in the men's 200 metre breaststroke and men's 400 metre breaststroke events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1894 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Russian male swimmers Category:Male breaststroke swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Russia Category:Swimmers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Saint Petersburg
